plugin vscode:
1. Live Preview
2. Live Server
3. Tailwind CSS Intellisense


1. create dir project
    mkdir learn_tailwind && cd learn_tailwind
2. installation tailwind
    npm init -y
        to generate file package.json
    npm install -D tailwindcss
    npx tailwindcss init
        this for initialization
    open tailwind.config.js
        set   content: [index.html],
    add tailwind directives at src/input.css (create new dir n file)
        @tailwind base;
        @tailwind components;
        @tailwind utilities;
    run scipt compile tailwind
        npx tailwindcss -i ./src/input.css -o ./dist/output.css --watch
        let it always running when we code / develop.
        or running script above when not running
    set css on website
    